channel.title: Read before posting in JavaScript
channel.description:
The Javascript example is here https://github.com/mazk5145/KeyAuth-JS-Example Please look at the videos on YouTube too https://youtube.com/KeyAuth

We will only assist with the default example that hasn't been changed, or added to your code. So, **do not** make a post if you're having issues adding KeyAuth to your code, only make an issue if KeyAuth is causing problems by myself. For other circumstances, you should use https://google.com or https://stackoverflow.com, or try adding your code to KeyAuth example instead of the other way around.
